main event: A cigar-shaped object with exhaust flame was observed over Keflavik International Airport, Iceland in November 1965.
interesting points: The object was visible for approximately 2 minutes and had no sound,The exhaust flame was bright and directed attention of observers,The object was initially at 6500' elevation and was seen moving in a straight line without any turns,All witnesses initially thought the object was a jet aircraft before concluding it was something else,An additional report from a Pan American 727 flight indicated the same sighting from a higher altitude.
witness description: Civilian and military personnel with good reliability
